<body>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="bodyshop-services-container">
      <section class="intro-section">
        <h1>Professional Services for Bodyshops</h1>
        <p>We offer independent and professional solutions tailored for vehicle repair centres — whether you're looking to improve your quoting accuracy, streamline documentation, or upskill your team.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="service-section">
        <h2>1. Damage Assessment & Reporting</h2>
        <p>Receive precise, independent assessments for accident repairs, lease returns, and insurance disputes. Our support includes photographic documentation, labour analysis, and parts pricing suggestions.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="service-section">
        <h2>2. Estimate Matching & Invoicing Support</h2>
        <p>We help bodyshops reconcile estimates with final invoices. Whether you use Audatex or GT Motive, our expertise can help reduce payment delays and claim queries.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="service-section">
        <h2>3. On-Site Technical Help & Training</h2>
        <p>We offer tailored support at your location: inspection days, live damage assessments, or process training. Our IMI-accredited assessor brings over 20 years of field experience.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="service-section">
        <h2>4. Onboarding & Collaboration</h2>
        <p>If you're interested in working with us, we’d love to hear from you. Reach out for a no-obligation conversation about how we can support your business.</p>
        <div class="contact-button">
          <a href="/contact">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
  </div>
